pageContext.claim: “Our Country is doing so well in so many ways. Great jobs numbers, with a record setting December. We are rebuilding our military. Vets finally have Choice & Accountability. Economy & GDP are strong. Tax & Reg cuts historic. Trade deals great. But we MUST fix our Southern Border!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump crams a lot into this tweet. The preliminary December job numbers were good, but not "record setting." More jobs have been added in a month at least five times since 2012. Plus, Trump's tax cut is not "historic." It's the eighth largest in U.S. history, falling behind two of Obama's.
